# Software Requirements

1. Node.js
2. npm (Node Package Manager)
3. MongoDB Community Server
4. VS Code
5. Git
6. GitHub Account
7. Web Browser (Chrome Recommended)

------------------------------------------------

# Backend Packages

express
mongoose
cors
dotenv
bcryptjs
jsonwebtoken
nodemon

Install using:

npm install express mongoose cors dotenv bcryptjs jsonwebtoken nodemon

------------------------------------------------

# Frontend Packages

react-router-dom
axios
bootstrap

Install using:

npm install axios react-router-dom bootstrap

------------------------------------------------

# System Requirements

Operating System:
- Windows / macOS / Linux

RAM:
- Minimum 4GB

Storage:
- Minimum 1GB Free Space

Internet:
- Required for package installation

------------------------------------------------

# Database Requirement

MongoDB Local Database

Connection String:

mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/blogplatform

------------------------------------------------

# Development Tools

- Visual Studio Code
- MongoDB Compass (Optional)
- Postman API Tester (Optional)

